all_answers.question: Pleaseee help I need a free verse poem for is your glass half full or glass half empty it’s due tmr!
all_answers.subject: English
all_answers.text:
Is your glass half full or half empty 
do you think its not enough or plenty 

drinking the glass with out no worry 
but the question comes to mind again 

was the glass half full or half empty
